    <p>And YOU can help!</p>
    <p>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death.</p>
    <p>Jen is no longer homeless and has figured out a solution:</p>
    <p>High-tech foam vests that are inexpensive, keep a person warm to 10 degrees below zero, help SAVE lives, and alleviate suffering.</p>
